6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Pipefy and Process Street share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Api Connections, Scheduling, Conditional Logic. Where Pipefy pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Error Handling, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Pipefy holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Process Street scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Pipefy offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Free, compared to Process Street's starting price of $100/mo. Pipefy has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Process Street does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
